Fight Yard Map - DARK DAY *Version 1

This is one of my maps I developed.
It is the first I released. There are still another ones in development.

About this map..:

It is a little fight yard map. There are many ways to hide und running arround. But the special thing on this map is, that the map is really dark. Any tiles of the map are lighted, but not enough.

I THINK, that this is a very cool map! Why? You can't see your enemies on the first time. It is REALLY funny to find them. :D


Players: 32 Spawns per Team
Lightning: Very dark
Developer/ Mapper: M!ndbyte
Arming: Buyzones in every Team, no Weapons laying arround in map.
